Sasalin suddenly went blind, trying to step back but found himself colliding with the branches, then falling to the ground. The monster seemed to clearly know where Sasalin had fallen, flying straight toward him and bringing the dark cloud with it.
"Kayer!" Tenuk shouted, flying out of the dark cloud, beginning to spiral around, trying to locate Nisi and Sasalin below in the darkness. "What should we do? Kayer...? Kayer, where are you?"
