"That was... this is one of the strangest shadow jumps I've ever done... Tanto Katerolon..." Kayer gasped for breath. Somehow, his eyes glowed with black light, and a surge of dark energy flowed within him. But just as Kayer was about to speak, his organic armor regained its color, and his eyes returned to their normal yellow.
After a while, Nisi finally understood what had happened. They all knew that Kayer possessed eerie shadow abilities, but he rarely used them because most people considered this ability extremely evil and terrifying. However, Nisi didn't know that Kayer could use this ability in any darkness. Moreover, from Kayer's reaction, he himself was also surprised.
