Now, the monster is motionless, and they can finally take a good look at what it really is. Its skin is dark and shiny, covered with a sticky layer of liquid, which is firmly attached to the monster's body. It has four wings and four legs, with long claws at the end of each leg, and two straight horns on its skull.
Before Tenuk and Kayer could even ask what this thing was, a monster screamed and darted out from the nearby bushes. At that moment, a familiar car crashed into the side of the monster, causing it to slide for a distance before stopping by Nisi's feet. Nisi didn't hesitate and grabbed a shotguns, firing a shot at the monster's head, killing it instantly.
